---
import PageLayout from '../layouts/PageLayout.astro';
---

<PageLayout title="Tentang Kami - SMKN 14 Jakarta">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 py-12">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-4" data-aos="fade-down">Tentang Kami</h1>
        <div class="w-24 h-1 bg-primary mx-auto mb-6"></div>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 leading-relaxed" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="100">
          SMK Negeri 14 Jakarta berkomitmen untuk mencetak generasi terampil, berkarakter, dan siap kerja di era industri 4.0.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center mb-16">
        <div data-aos="fade-right">
          <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/600x400/1D4ED8/FFFFFF?text=Visi+Misi+SMKN+14"
               alt="Visi dan Misi SMKN 14 Jakarta"
               class="rounded-xl shadow-lg w-full">
        </div>
        <div data-aos="fade-left">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-4">Visi Kami</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 mb-6 leading-relaxed">
            Menjadi sekolah kejuruan unggulan yang menghasilkan lulusan kompeten, berdaya saing global, dan berkontribusi nyata bagi pembangunan bangsa.
          </p>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-4">Misi Kami</h2>
          <ul class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 space-y-2">
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary mr-3 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
              </svg>
              Menyelenggarakan pendidikan kejuruan yang berkualitas
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary mr-3 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
              </svg>
              Mengembangkan kompetensi siswa sesuai kebutuhan industri
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary mr-3 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
              </svg>
              Membangun karakter dan kepribadian yang kuat
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-primary/5 dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-xl p-8" data-aos="fade-up">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-4 text-center">Nilai-Nilai Kami</h2>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 text-center">
          <div>
            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-primary rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
              <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-2">Inovatif</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">Selalu mengikuti perkembangan teknologi terbaru</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-secondary rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
              <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-gray-900" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 20h5v-2a3 3 0 00-5.356-1.857M17 20H7m10 0v-2c0-.656-.126-1.283-.356-1.857M7 20H2v-2a3 3 0 015.356-1.857M7 20v-2c0-.656.126-1.283.356-1.857m0 0a5.002 5.002 0 019.288 0M15 7a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0zm6 3a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0zM7 10a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0z"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-2">Kolaboratif</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">Bekerja sama dengan industri dan masyarakat</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-accent rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
              <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-2">Berintegritas</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">Menjunjung tinggi kejujuran dan tanggung jawab</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</PageLayout>